tps://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32014461&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=110620884368a97c3caee333_68878537"/><published>2025-08-23T16:04:41+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>80fbd1fd79687438b7af681594633b60</id><title>近400呎市區銀主居屋僅「2字頭」推拍 呎價低至6000元</title><updated>2025-08-23T16:05:21+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-23T16:05:21+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573706018"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573706018"&gt;環亞物業拍賣將於下周二(26日)推拍黃大仙鳯鑽苑高層2室，實用面積約376方呎，於未補價第二市場開價228萬元，呎價約6,064元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;該單位亦以338萬元已補價自由市場價拍賣，呎價約8,989元。物業在個別銀行網上估價約459萬元，是次開拍價低約121萬元，差幅約26.4%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：近400呎市區銀主居屋僅「2字頭」推拍呎價低至6000元 | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250823%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250823142246475-0823_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=c4c24ebc103de2691c713d5c9ad15bfb&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32014462&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=110620884368a97c3caee333_68878537"/><published>2025-08-23T16:05:21+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3a98553440ebf57d6d5cdafb6d7e28ac</id><title>結業潮｜凍肉店難頂高昂「皮費」 門市網店全線結業</title><updated>2025-08-23T16:05:55+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-23T16:05:55+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573706026"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573706026"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3997977%2F%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%25BD%25AE%25EF%25BD%259C%25E5%2587%258D%25E8%2582%2589%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%259B%25A3%25E9%25A0%2582%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2598%2582%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%259A%25AE%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=84798c31c343662b779189e3f1e1e142&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3997 ...門市網店全線結業?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;【結業/執笠/開業/新店】在經營成本上升、市民購買力下降下，結業潮仍持續，尤其對於小商戶而言，經營更加困難。日前再有一間人氣凍肉店因「皮費」太高而生意額不足宣布門市、網店齊齊於8月23日結業，更無奈表示是「損手離場」，用「光榮結業」似乎不太適合。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;位於深水埗大埔道的食材店Mr. Cool，一直以入口凍肉、生果為主，並以平靚正，薄利多銷，批發價等於零售價為宗旨。店主日前於Facebook公布，門市及網店均於8月23日齊齊結業，並進行3日的執笠清貨大減價。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;▼點擊圖片放大&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;+8&lt;br/&gt;店主發長文交待結業原因，表示門市及網店經營都相當困難，別以為網店成交較低，但其實「皮費」亦好高，例如倉租、電費、勞保、運輸等等，更表示凍肉這一行愈來愈嚟難做，就算0頂手都冇人問津，亦明白無人願意頂手原因：生意唔好、客人購買力又弱、租約又未完、基本皮費又重，每個月電費都2皮、一年一度勞保又4皮，所以網店、門市都好難做。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32014466&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=110620884368a97c3caee333_68878537"/><published>2025-08-23T16:05:55+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f24b8e9834912ce9592a0d8ada8c2557</id><title>🆘蝕讓成交｜西貢全幢屋呎價低見5,548元 業主6年蝕349萬元 蒸發23％樓價</title><updated>2025-08-23T16:06:34+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-23T16:06:34+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573706035"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573706035"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3997980%2F%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25EF%25BD%259C%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A2%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25A6%258B5%2C548%25E5%2585%2583%2520%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%259D%2595349%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%2520%25E8%2592%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC23%25EF%25BC%2585%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=805eab8038ac494b906507e539d6da9d&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3997 ... 元 蒸發23％樓價?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;西世紀21奇豐物業西貢區營業董事廖振雄表示，新近錄得西貢蠔涌新村單號村屋成交，建築面積2,100平方呎，3房(1套) 2廳間隔，連天台約700呎，原叫價1,298萬元，累減133萬元，減近10.2%，以1,165萬元獲買家承接，建築面積呎價5,548元，低市價5%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據了解，原業主於2019年7月購入上址，當時作價1,514萬元，持貨6年至今易手，賬面虧蝕349萬元，單位期內跌幅23%。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32014467&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=110620884368a97c3caee333_68878537"/><published>2025-08-23T16:06:34+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>31428764c976ef2ead16aec1f2bf0def</id><title>🆘🆘7月新盤撻訂183宗按月升7% 錦上路柏瓏撻111伙「完勝」其他新盤</title><updated>2025-08-23T16:07:15+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-23T16:07:15+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573706038"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573706038"&gt;樓市gogogo&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😆&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😆&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😆&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;2025年7月新盤市場共錄得183宗撻訂個案，較6月的171宗升12宗或7%，涉及撻訂金額約逾1.62億元，較上月1.76億萬元減少近8%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;最大一宗撻訂個案為何文田站上蓋瑜一第IC期三房單位，買家逾兩年半後棄購，終輸近200萬元訂金。同時錦上路站項目柏瓏單月111宗撻訂個案，涉及撻訂金額1.09億元，再次屬成為「撻訂王」。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址: 7月新盤撻訂183宗按月升7%錦上路柏瓏撻111伙「完勝」其他新盤 | 香港01 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F60269077%3Futm_source%3D01articlecopy%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=7ab51d98b61bd294d27c05fa64fdca1b&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/602 ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32014468&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=110620884368a97c3caee333_68878537"/><published>2025-08-23T16:07:15+08:00</published></entry></feed>